quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  50,30,"That Day We ask Hell, \"Are you full?\" And it asks, \"Are there any more"
  50,31,"And the Garden [of Paradise] is brought near for the pious and righteous, and it is no longer a distant objective [for them]"
  50,32,"This is what you were promised. [And this is what was promised] to every one who turned (to Allah in sincere repentance) and protected (himself against satanic influence)"
  50,33,"Who feared the Gracious One without physically seeing Him with worldly eyes, and has come with a mind turned in devotion (to Him)"
  50,34,"Enter therein [in Paradise] in Peace and Security; this is time of eternal life"
  50,35,"There is for them therein all that they desire. And [there is besides] much more with Us"
  50,36,"And how many a generation before them, stronger in power than they, did We destroy! They had wandered through the lands in search of a place of escape"
  50,37,Certainly indeed in this is a lesson to learn for any who has an understanding mind or who lends an insightful ear
  50,38,We created the heavens and the earth and all things in between in six periods of time. And weariness did not even touch Us
  50,39,"Have patience, then, over what they say, and glorify your Lord with praise, before the rising of the sun and before its setting"
  50,40,"And glorify Him during parts of the night, and post prostrations"
  50,41,"And listen the Day when the Caller calls out from a place quite near, —"
  50,42,The Day when they hear a real mighty Blast — that is the Day of Resurrection
  50,43,It is indeed We Who give life and cause death; and to Us is the final destination
  50,44,That Day the earth swiftly separates from them. That gathering — it is easy for Us
  50,45,We know what they say! And you are not to be coercive on them. So admonish with the Qur'an such as fear My Warning